{"tid":2253612,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 電影  ~～食人劇場～～22/10上","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T09:57:39.000Z","uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"570eeca3f695f53a603d4678639fa71a9cdcf295","tid":2253612,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ILhMvdHnuSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FILhMvdHnuSo&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=58305c4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ILhMvdHnuSo</a><br />\n<br />\n《食人劇場》背景設定於核災發生後，所有人因災難陷入饑荒，劇情聚焦於 Leonora （《 浩劫奇蹟》吉特維特 飾演）一家三口，她和丈夫 Jacob（《不可能的逃亡》湯瑪斯古勒斯塔 飾演）以及女兒 Alice 處境堪慮，所幸某日，當地旅館邀請所有倖存者前往觀看劇場演出，並附贈一份美味晚餐，希望以慈善活動為名，協助所有陷入困境的災民， Leonora 一家依約前往旅館，並遵從旅館的話，戴上金色面具和演員有所區隔，沒想到表演開始後，觀眾卻一個個消失，現實和戲劇的界線逐漸變得模糊，而 Leonora 的 Alice 也不見蹤影&hellip;&hellip;。"},{"pid":"a7406475736d62599874bf4f15144e870671ec96","tid":2253612,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:25:15.000Z","msg":"似乎幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13d2cde7d6750d20da82be401eebbad084751ff","tid":2253612,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"依加睇下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f345b6466851904922d12ff8096687fd05d23562","tid":2253612,"uid":10056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"係咁慢鏡唔知做乜9"},{"pid":"aa3650db567f9bb7ed23c3186866037a032abc3e","tid":2253612,"uid":153689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"睇完淨係覺得好撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf76a86eae45d6239f86c3c0ed7607649a7c2019","tid":2253612,"uid":225422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"好假"},{"pid":"66fdc94534365f6b6ceb8fe